Building SDL3_shadercross for UWP (WinRT)
-----------------------------------------
SDL3_shadercross uses Visual Studio 2022 to build for UWP.

Dependencies
------------
Before building, download SDL3's UWP source code:

https://github.com/FNA-NET/SDL3-uwp

Place it as a sibling folder to SDL_shadercross:
  ../SDL3-uwp/

Compiling
---------
1. Build SDL3-uwp/VisualC-WinRT/SDL-UWP.sln
2. Build SDL_shadercross.sln
3. Grab SDL3_shadercross.dll and SDL3.dll, ship it!
